-- Sarkozy to Seek Second Term in France
-- B y   V i d y a   R o o t
-- 2012-02-15T19:11:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-15/sarkozy-will-seek-french-re-election-playing-euro-crisis-leadership-card.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
said he will seek a second term as president.  He made the announcement on TF1 television. The first round
of French elections are scheduled for April 22, with the second
and decisive round set for May 6.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
